data.description: Spacious bungalow in Manchester's Southeast Somerville neighborhood with 4 bedrooms, dining room and a large living room with newer systems including a 2 year old furnace & water heater, 5 year old roof and low maintenance vinyl siding! Property features central air, two first floor bedrooms & bathroom, galley style kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel refrigerator, gas range and hardwood floors. Basement has been partially finished with lots of potential. Small private fenced back yard as a bonus perfect to wind down. Weekend showings only. Sale subject to seller finding suitable housing. Showings resume on 9/30 (Saturdays & Sundays only).
